  13:Driver/timer_driver.c ****  *    dma_cb_table = 16 x 4 = 64 bytes
  14:Driver/timer_driver.c ****  *    mode_table   = 16 x 1 = 16 bytes
  15:Driver/timer_driver.c ****  *    dma_ch_table = 16 x 4 = 64 bytes
  16:Driver/timer_driver.c ****  *    ──────────────────────────────
  17:Driver/timer_driver.c ****  *    Tổng         = 208 bytes
